      <title>克里夫·阿斯尼斯（Cliff Asness）的AQR猛烈抨击“投资失败”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/cliff-asness-s-aqr-slams-buffer-etf-boom-on-investment-failure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AQR Capital Management违反了期权驱动的资金的兴起，这些资金限制了股票下跌期间损失的损失，声称这种不断增长的投资组合保险形式可提供较低的回报＆Mdash;有更多风险＆mdash;而不是简单的替代方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/cliff-asness-s-aqr-slams-buffer-etf-boom-on-investment-failure</guid>
